Package: cvMAGIC
Title: Cross-Validated, Per-Module-Adaptive MAGIC with Bootstrap Uncertainty
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Annice Najafi [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Annice Najafi <annicenajafi27@gmail.com>
Description: Native R implementation of MAGIC (Markov Affinity-based Graph
    Imputation of Cells, van Dijk et al. 2018) with three additions: (1)
    Batson-style molecular cross-validation to select the diffusion time
    objectively, (2) per-gene-module adaptive diffusion time to mitigate
    over-smoothing, and (3) bootstrap-based per-(cell, gene) standard errors.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    Matrix,
    RANN,
    irlba,
    stats
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
